Package com.credenceid.face

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FaceEngine
    This interface contains all methods related to face detection, recognition, and matching.
    FaceEngine.OnAnalyzeFaceImageListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a request to FaceEngine.analyzeFace(Bitmap, OnAnalyzeFaceImageListener) or FaceEngine.analyzeFace(byte[], int, int, OnAnalyzeFaceImageListener) has finished.
    FaceEngine.OnCreateFaceTemplateListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a request to FaceEngine.createFaceTemplate(Bitmap, OnCreateFaceTemplateListener) or FaceEngine.createFaceTemplate(byte[], int, int, OnCreateFaceTemplateListener) has finished.
    FaceEngine.OnDetectFaceListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a request to FaceEngine.detectFace(Bitmap, OnDetectFaceListener) or FaceEngine.detectFace(byte[], int, int, OnDetectFaceListener) hash finished.
    FaceEngine.OnMatchFaceTemplatesListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a request to FaceEngine.compareFace(byte[], byte[], OnMatchFaceTemplatesListener) has finished.
    FaceEngine.OnVerifyFaceLiveness
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a request to FaceEngine.verifyFaceLiveness( Uri video, OnVerifyFaceLiveness) has finished.

    FaceView
    This class can be used to draw a detected faces's RectF and landmark coordinate points onto an image with ease, without having to worry about math, scaling, or resizing.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FaceEngine.Emotion
    Different emotions recognized by FaceEngine.
    FaceEngine.Gender
    Different genders that are recognized by FaceEngine.
    FaceEngine.HeadPoseDirection
    Different head pose directions, in human understandable format.
